If we wanted to simplify it,

54
00:02:56.000 --> 00:02:58.000
we could say remove collision,

55
00:02:58.000 --> 00:03:02.000
make the whole count to max-hole vertices 8,

56
00:03:02.000 --> 00:03:06.000
hull precision 10,000, hit apply,

57
00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:11.000
and there we are with a simpler piece of collision geometry.

58
00:03:11.000 --> 00:03:14.000
This is different from the other cart over here,

59
00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:18.000
where the collision data was actually brought over from its origin,

60
00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:20.000
I believe in 3ds Max.

61
00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:25.000
And you can see the way this was modeled

