00:03:25.000 --> 00:03:30.000
is quite different from how Unreal Engine would automatically process this kind of data.

63
00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:35.000
For our simple wall,

64
00:03:35.000 --> 00:03:38.000
we might want to see what the existing collision data is,

65
00:03:38.000 --> 00:03:41.000
