66
00:03:41.000 --> 00:03:44.000
That's because this does not actually have any collision data.

67
00:03:44.000 --> 00:03:47.000
We have no primitives, no convex elements.

68
00:03:47.000 --> 00:03:50.000
What's happening here is we have collision complexity

69
00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:53.000
