72
00:04:03.000 --> 00:04:07.000
It would be much more expensive if we did something like that with the colonnade here.

73
00:04:07.000 --> 00:04:10.000
So we went down to the same thing and said,

74
00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:16.000
collision complexity, use complex collision as simple and save that.

75
00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:20.000
We could test to see that it's working with player collision.

76
00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:22.000
And now we're putting a lot more load on the CPU,

77
00:04:22.000 --> 00:04:27.000
even though it's very unlikely if we've got a standard third-person game, for example.

